title: 2009 Florida Gators baseball team
text:
The 2009 Florida Gators baseball team represented the <a href="University%20of%20Florida">University of Florida</a> in the sport of <a href="baseball">baseball</a> during the <a href="2009%20NCAA%20Division%20I%20baseball%20season">2009 college baseball season</a>. The Gators competed in <a href="Division%20I%20%28NCAA%29">Division I</a> of the <a href="National%20Collegiate%20Athletic%20Association">National Collegiate Athletic Association</a> (NCAA) and the Eastern Division of the <a href="Southeastern%20Conference">Southeastern Conference</a> (SEC). They played their home games at <a href="Alfred%20A.%20McKethan%20Stadium">Alfred A. McKethan Stadium</a>, on the university's <a href="Gainesville%2C%20Florida">Gainesville, Florida</a> campus. The team was coached by <a href="Kevin%20O%27Sullivan%20%28baseball%29">Kevin O'Sullivan</a>, who was in his second season at Florida.
